ng>Rack Comes in Two Sizes: Compact and Full Size</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>No Front Wheel Removal</li><a href=\"http://www.pipelineracks.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/features-pic.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.pipelineracks.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/features-pic.jpg\" alt=\"features-pic\" width=\"561\" height=\"369\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-187\" /></a>\r\n<li>No Holes to Drill</li>\r\n<li>Simple Installation</li>\r\n<li>Fits in all Truck Beds and Under Tonneau Cover</li>\r\n<li>Use as a Garage or Trailer Bike Rack</li>\r\n<li>Works with Mountain, Road, Cruisers and More</li>\r\n<li>Compact Size Rack comes in 2 and 3 Bike Option</li>\r\n<li>Full Size Rack comes in 2, 3, 4, and 5 Bike Option</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p> <br /><strong>Tire Arms Comes in Two Styles: Standard and Add-A-Bike .</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Bike rack only contacts rubber tire (not rim or frame)</li>\r\n<li>The rack arms adjusts for 24 inch to 29 inch diameter tires</li>\r\n<li>The rack arms adjusts to fit .75 to 2.8 inch widetires</li>\r\n<li>Holds Bike Tire Securely in Three Places</li>\r\n<li>Tire acts as an insulator to vibration during transportation</li>\r\n<li>Rack \"arms\" design fully adjustable to maximize bike stability</li>\r\n<li>Rack arms allow clearance for disk brakes systems</li>\r\n<li>Features a wheelie Bar to secure both front and rear tires</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Rack is constructed from thin wall steel tubing for high strength, durability, and light weight with a Powder Coated Finish.</p>\";}','yes'),('234','wonderplugin-gridgallery-engine','WordPress Grid Gallery Plugin','yes'),('235','wonderplugin_gridgallery_userrole','manage_options','yes'),('236','wonderplugin_gridgallery_thumbnailsize','medium','yes'),('277','cpto_options','a:3:{s:8:\"autosort\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"adminsort\";s:0:\"\";s:10:\"capability\";s:13:\"switch_themes\";}','yes'),('281','tto_options','a:3:{s:8:\"autosort\";s:1:\"1\";s:9:\"adminsort\";s:1:\"1\";s:5:\"level\";s:1:\"8\";}','yes'),('283',