a width of at least 41 inches, but not greater than 49 inches will fit the two bike rack sub compact rack</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-8\">\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>49 inches = Compact Bike Rack</strong>\r\n\r\nTrucks with a width of at least 49 inches but not greater than 59 inches will fit the compact bike rack. The compact rack comes in two sizes that holds either 2 or 3 bikes.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>59 inches = Full Size Bike Rack</strong>\r\n\r\nTrucks with a width of at least 59 inches will fit the full size bike rack. The full size rack comes in 3 sizes. It holds either a 3, 4 or 5 bikes. The best part is that if you buy a 3 bike rack you can always buy extra arms later to make it a 4 or 5 bike rack.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br />','Fit Guide','','publish','open','open','','fit_guide','','','2014-12-30 01:03:21','2014-12-30 01:03:21','','0','http://pipelineracks.com/?page_id=20','9','page','','0'),('22','1','2014-11-08 14:31:18','2014-11-08 14:31:18','','Fit Guide','','inherit','open','open','','20-revision-v1','','','2014-11-08 14:31:18','2014-11-08 14:31:18','','20','http://pipelineracks.com/%taxonomy%/postname%/','0','revision','','0'),('23','1','2014-11-08 14:32:12','2014-11-08 14:32:12','Installation is easy. Just follow the instructions that come with the bike rack. Below are pictures that show how easy the installation is.<strong> Note:</strong> a cable lock should always be used in transporting any bike. Both for theft and security incase of an accident.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">Please click on photo below for detail instructions.</span>\r\n<a href=\"http://pipelineracks.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Installing_-the-_strap.pdf\"><img src=\"http://www.pipelineracks.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/installtion.jpg\" alt=\"installtion\" width=\"600\" height=\"500\" class=\"img-responsive alignnone size-full wp-image-214\" /></a>','Installation','','publish','open','open','','installation','','','2015-03-20 17:14:30','2015-03-20 17:14:30','','0','http://pipelineracks.com/?page_id=23','8','page','','0'),('24','1','2014-11-08 14:32:12','2014-11-08 14:32:12','','Instasllations','','inherit','open','open','','23-revision-v1','','','2014-11-08 14:32:12','2014-11-08 14:32:12','','23','http://pipelineracks.com/%taxonomy%/postname%/','0','revision','','0'),('25','1','2014-11-08 14:32:59','2014-11-08 14:32:59','<strong>Q: Does the rack come with a cable lock?</strong>\r\n\r\nA: No, the best option is to purchase one locally.\r\n\r\n<strong>Q: How is the rack mounted to a hard surface?</strong>\r\n\r\nA: A optional mounting kit is available that connects mounting \"feet\" of the rack. The feet have two holes per feet on each side that allow .25\" bolts to mount the rack to any surface you can drill a hole through. Great for trailers!\r\n\r\n<strong>Q: My rack arrived and it is missing pieces?</strong>\r\n\r\nA: Just let us know what pieces you are missing and we will ship them to you.\r\n\r\n<strong>Q: What is the 30 Day money back guarantee?</strong>\r\n\r\nA: Just that, if you are not satisfied with the product you can return it within 30 days of purchase.\r\n\r\n<strong>Q: What is the adjustment range for tire width</strong>\r\n\r\nA: The arms can adjust for .75 to 2.80 inch wide tires\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nLet us know if you have any other questions, by emailing <a href=\"mailto:Info@PipelineRacks.com\">Info@PipelineRacks.com</a>','FAQs','','publish','open','open','','faqs','','','2014-12-05 11:04:50','2014-12-05 11:04:50','','0','http://pipelineracks.com/?page_id=25','7','page','','0'),('27','1','2014-11-08 14:32:59','2014-11-08 14:32:59','<strong>Q: Does the rack come with a cable lock?</strong>\r\n\r\nA: No, the best option is to purchase one locally.\r\n\r\n<strong>Q: How is the rack mounted to a hard surface?</strong>\r\n\r\nA: A optional mounting kit is available that connects mounting \"feet\" of the rack. The feet have two holes per feet 